  ('seaside-apartment', 'Seaside Apartment', 'Квартира у моря', 'Seaside Apartment — your perfect stay right by the sea. 
Only 1 minute walk to the beach, with a direct sea view from the balcony. The apartment is fully equipped for a comfortable stay: cozy bed, washing machine, dishwasher, linens, towels, toiletries, beautiful tableware, full kitchen, and floor heating.
Enjoy the sea-view balcony — perfect for morning coffee, sunsets, and relaxing evenings with the sound of the waves.', 'Seaside Apartment — идеальный вариант для отдыха у самого моря. 
До пляжа — всего 1 минута пешком, море видно прямо с балкона. Пространство продумано для комфортного проживания: удобная кровать, стиральная и посудомоечная машины, постельное бельё и полотенца, средства гигиены, красивая посуда, полноценная кухня и тёплый пол.
Балкон с видом на море — место для кофе, закатов и расслабленных вечеров под шум волн.', 41.63528, 41.60825, 1, 2, 1, 4, '["/apartments/seaside-apartment/01.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/02.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/03.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/04.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/05.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/06.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/07.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/08.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/09.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/10.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/11.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/12.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/13.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/14.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/15.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/16.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/17.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/18.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/19.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/20.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/21.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/22.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/23.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/24.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/25.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/26.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/27.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/28.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/29.jpg", "/apartments/seaside-apartment/30.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Sofa bed", "Queen bed"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Living room", "photos": 5, "amenities": ["Sofa bed"]}, {"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 4, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Dining area", "photos": 3, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Bedroom", "photos": 5, "amenities": ["Queen bed"]}, {"room": "Full bathroom", "photos": 6, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Balcony", "photos": 5, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Exterior", "photos": 4, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Additional photos", "photos": 3, "amenities": []}]'::jsonb, '904091122937932973'),
  ('alliance-burgundy-8th-floor', 'Alliance Burgundy 8th floor by brege', 'Alliance Burgundy 8-й этаж от brege', 'These elegant apartments in a premium building are ideal for business trips or vacations. Bright, spacious, and modern, they feature a high-quality renovation.

Located in the city center, the apartment accommodates up to four guests, with a separate bedroom and large living area with a fully equipped kitchen. Enjoy stunning views of the sea, city, and mountains, perfect for a relaxing breakfast.', 'Эти элегантные апартаменты в здании премиум-класса идеально подходят для деловых поездок или отдыха. Светлые, просторные и современные, с качественным ремонтом.

Квартира расположена в центре города и вмещает до четырех гостей, с отдельной спальней и большой гостиной с полностью оборудованной кухней. Наслаждайтесь потрясающим видом на море, город и горы, идеально подходящие для расслабляющего завтрака.', 41.6418, 41.6157, 1, 2, 1, 4, '["/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/01.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/02.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/03.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/04.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/05.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/06.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/07.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/08.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/09.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/10.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/11.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/12.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/13.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/14.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/15.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/16.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/17.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/18.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/19.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/20.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/21.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/22.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/23.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/24.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/25.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/26.jpg", "/apartments/alliance-burgundy-8th-floor/27.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Sofa bed", "Air conditioning", "Heating", "TV", "Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Coffee", "Microwave", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle", "Dining table", "Queen bed", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Iron", "Body soap", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo", "Washer"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Living room", "photos": 3, "amenities": ["Sofa bed", "Air conditioning", "Heating", "TV"]}, {"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Coffee", "Microwave", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle"]}, {"room": "Dining area", "photos": 4, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Dining table", "Air conditioning", "Heating"]}, {"room": "Bedroom", "photos": 7, "amenities": ["Queen bed", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Iron", "Heating", "Air conditioning", "TV"]}, {"room": "Full bathroom", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Body soap", "Hot water", "Heating", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo"]}, {"room": "Balcony", "photos": 5, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Laundry area", "photos": 1, "amenities": ["Washer"]}, {"room": "Additional photos", "photos": 3, "amenities": []}]'::jsonb, '1179731395304757203'),
  ('white-camelia-apartment', 'White Camelia apartment by brege', 'Апартаменты White Camelia от Brege', 'Welcome to our brand-new studio, located on the ground floor of a beautifully restored historic building in the heart of the city. This stylish and cozy space is perfect for travelers looking for comfort and convenience.

Situated in the historic center, you’ll be just steps away from the city''s best cafes, restaurants, and , and cultural attractions. Enjoy the charm of old architecture combined with modern amenities in this unique space!

Book your stay and experience the magic of the city! ✨', 'Добро пожаловать в нашу совершенно новую студию, расположенную на первом этаже красиво отреставрированного исторического здания в самом сердце города. Это стильное и уютное жилье идеально подходит для путешественников, ищущих комфорт и удобство.

Жилье расположено в историческом центре всего в нескольких шагах от лучших кафе, ресторанов и культурных достопримечательностей города. Насладитесь очарованием старой архитектуры в сочетании с современными удобствами в этом уникальном жилье!

Забронируйте жилье и почувствуйте волшебство города! ✨', 41.6499, 41.6429, 0, 1, 1, 2, '["/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/01.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/02.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/03.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/04.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/05.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/06.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/07.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/08.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/09.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/10.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/11.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/12.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/13.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/14.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/15.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/16.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/17.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/18.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/19.jpg", "/apartments/white-camelia-apartment/20.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["King bed", "Air conditioning", "Clothing storage", "Heating", "TV", "Essentials", "Bed linens", "Room-darkening shades", "Hangers", "Iron", "Patio or balcony", "Cooking basics", "Wine glasses", "Body soap", "Hot water", "Coffee", "Kitchen", "Microwave", "Private entrance", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Dedicated workspace", "Washer", "Refrigerator", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo", "Wifi"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 2, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Dining area", "photos": 2, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Bedroom", "photos": 9, "amenities": ["King bed", "Air conditioning", "Clothing storage", "Heating", "TV", "Essentials", "Bed linens", "Room-darkening shades", "Hangers", "Iron", "Patio or balcony", "Cooking basics", "Wine glasses", "Body soap", "Hot water", "Coffee", "Kitchen", "Microwave", "Private entrance", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Dedicated workspace", "Washer", "Refrigerator", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo", "Wifi"]}, {"room": "Ful