  ('coral-apartment', 'Coral Apartment by brege', 'Квартира Coral от brege', 'Welcome to our cozy studio, perfect for your vacation or business trip. The spacious and bright room is designed in a modern style, creating a pleasant atmosphere. The fully equipped kitchen has everything you need to prepare your own meals. You can enjoy free Wi-Fi and comfort thanks to the air conditioning. 

One of the studio''s main advantages is its convenient location. It’s just a two-minute walk to the sea, allowing you to easily enjoy the beach and coastal views.', 'Добро пожаловать в нашу уютную студию, идеально подходящую для отдыха или деловой поездки. Просторная и светлая комната оформлена в современном стиле, создавая приятную атмосферу. Полностью оборудованная кухня оснащена всем необходимым для приготовления собственных блюд. К услугам гостей бесплатный Wi-Fi и комфорт благодаря кондиционеру. 

Одним из главных преимуществ студии является ее удобное расположение. Всего в двух минутах ходьбы от моря, что позволяет легко насладиться пляжем и видами на побережье.', 41.635, 41.6073, 0, 1, 1, 2, '["/apartments/coral-apartment/01.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/02.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/03.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/04.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/05.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/06.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/07.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/08.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/09.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/10.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/11.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/12.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/13.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/14.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/15.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/16.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/17.jpg", "/apartments/coral-apartment/18.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Coffee", "Coffee maker", "Freezer", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle", "Dining table", "Queen bed", "Air conditioning", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "TV", "Iron", "Body soap", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo", "Patio or balcony"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Coffee", "Coffee maker", "Freezer", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle"]}, {"room": "Dining area", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Dining table"]}, {"room": "Bedroom", "photos": 4, "amenities": ["Queen bed", "Air conditioning", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "TV", "Iron"]}, {"room": "Full bathroom", "photos": 4, "amenities": ["Body soap", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo"]}, {"room": "Balcony", "photos": 5, "amenities": ["Patio or balcony"]}, {"room": "Additional photos", "photos": 1, "amenities": []}]'::jsonb, '1374696469966790089'),
  ('granat-apartment', 'Granat Apartment by brege', 'Granat Apartment от brege', 'Welcome to this elegant and newly furnished one-bedroom apartment located on the 12th floor of ORBI City D2 — the newest and most modern tower in the prestigious ORBI City complex in Batumi. 
From the balcony, you can enjoy a beautiful view of the Black Sea and the vibrant Heroes’ Alley - one of the most scenic and iconic parts of modern Batumi.
Perfect for couples, solo travelers, families or business guests looking for a stylish, clean and well-located place to stay in Batumi.', 'Добро пожаловать в эту элегантную и недавно меблированную квартиру с одной спальней, расположенную на 12-м этаже ORBI City D2 — новейшей и самой современной башни в престижном комплексе ORBI City в Батуми. 
С балкона открывается прекрасный вид на Черное море и оживленную Аллею Героев — одну из самых живописных и знаковых частей современного Батуми.
Идеально подходит для пар, одиночных путешественников, семей или деловых гостей, которые ищут стильное, чистое и удобно расположенное жилье в Батуми.', 41.6391, 41.6157, 1, 1, 1, 4, '["/apartments/granat-apartment/01.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/02.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/03.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/04.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/05.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/06.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/07.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/08.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/09.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/10.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/11.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/12.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/13.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/14.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/15.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/16.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/17.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/18.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/19.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/20.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/21.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/22.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/23.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/24.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/25.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/26.jpg", "/apartments/granat-apartment/27.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["King bed", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Air conditioning", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Essentials", "TV", "Iron", "Body soap", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Living room", "photos": 4, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 3, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Dining area", "photos": 4, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Bedroom", "photos": 5, "amenities": ["King bed", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Air conditioning", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Essentials", "TV", "Iron"]}, {"room": "Full bathroom", "photos": 4, "amenities": ["Body soap", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo"]}, {"room"