  ('cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi', 'Cozy View apartment in Old Batumi by brege', 'Уютная квартира с видом в Старом Батуми от brege', 'Welcome to a stylish studio located in the heart of Batumi’s historic Old Town! From your window, enjoy breathtaking views of the cathedral, the mountains, and the city skyline — a perfect setting for those who appreciate beauty and atmosphere.
Step outside and find yourself surrounded by Batumi’s best cafes, restaurants, and bars. All major attractions — Piazza, Alphabet Tower, the Boulevard, the cable car, and more — are just a short walk away.', 'Добро пожаловать в стильную студию, расположенную в центре исторического Старого города Батуми! Из окон открывается потрясающий вид на собор, горы и город — идеальное место для тех, кто ценит красоту и атмосферу.
Выйдите на улицу, и вы окажетесь в окружении лучших кафе, ресторанов и баров Батуми. До всех основных достопримечательностей — площади, Башни Алфавита, бульвара, канатной дороги и многого другого — можно дойти пешком.', 41.64501, 41.6359, 0, 2, 1, 3, '["/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/01.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/02.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/03.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/04.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/05.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/06.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/07.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/08.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/09.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/10.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/11.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/12.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/13.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/14.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/15.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/16.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/17.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/18.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/19.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/20.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/21.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/22.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/23.jpg", "/apartments/cozy-view-apartment-in-old-batumi/24.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Sofa bed", "Air conditioning", "Wifi", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Iron", "Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle", "Dining table", "Double bed", "Extra pillows and blankets", "TV", "Body soap", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Living room