  ('modern-batumi-apartment', 'Modern Batumi apartment by brege', 'Современная квартира в Батуми от Brege', 'Stylish modern apartment in one of Batumi’s most desirable locations. 
A bright, airy space with floor-to-ceiling windows and lots of natural light. The interior is modern and thoughtfully designed. 
Just a 10-minute walk to the sea and the Batumi Boulevard. Surrounded by top restaurants, boutiques, green spaces, and key attractions.', 'Стильная современная квартира в одном из самых желанных мест Батуми. 
Светлое, просторное помещение с окнами от пола до потолка и естественным освещением. Интерьер современный и продуманный. 
Всего в 10 минутах ходьбы от моря и бульвара Батуми. В окружении лучших ресторанов, бутиков, зеленых насаждений и главных достопримечательностей.', 41.63867, 41.62775, 1, 2, 1, 3, '["/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/01.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/02.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/03.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/04.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/05.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/06.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/07.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/08.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/09.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/10.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/11.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/12.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/13.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/14.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/15.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/16.jpg", "/apartments/modern-batumi-apartment/17.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Sofa bed", "Air conditioning", "Heating", "Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Coffee", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Dishwasher", "Toaster", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle", "Dining table", "Double bed", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Iron", "Body soap", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo", "Washer", "Dryer"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Living room", "photos": 3, "amenities": ["Sofa bed", "Air conditioning", "Heating"]}, {"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 3, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Coffee", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Dishwasher", "Toaster", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle"]}, {"room": "Dining area", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Air conditioning", "Dining table", "Heating"]}, {"room": "Bedroom", "photos": 3, "amenities": ["Double bed", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Air conditioning", "Heating", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Iron"