  ('batumi-view-and-vibes', 'Batumi View and Vibes by brege', 'Батуми: виды и атмосфера', 'Our stylish and cozy apartment is all about your calm and comfort — cool even on the hottest days (no direct sunlight here), sea view + wave soundtrack 24/7, balcony for slow sips and salty breeze. 
Few steps from the beach, a short stroll to cafes, and always kissed by the sound of the sea.', 'Наша стильная и уютная квартира создана для вашего спокойствия и комфорта — прохладно даже в самые жаркие дни (здесь нет прямых солнечных лучей), вид на море + звуки волн 24/7, балкон для медленных глотков и соленого бриза. 
В нескольких шагах от пляжа, в нескольких минутах ходьбы от кафе, и всегда слышен шум моря.', 41.623, 41.5933, 1, 2, 1, 4, '["/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/01.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/02.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/03.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/04.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/05.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/06.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/07.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/08.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/09.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/10.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/11.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/12.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/13.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/14.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/15.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/16.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/17.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/18.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/19.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/20.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/21.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/22.jpg", "/apartments/batumi-view-and-vibes/23.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Sofa bed", "Air conditioning", "TV", "Wifi", "Beach essentials", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Resort access", "Elevator", "Clothing storage", "Waterfront", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Microwave", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle", "Dining table", "Washer", "Cleaning products", "Queen bed", "Hangers", "Iron", "Drying rack for clothing", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Shampoo", "Body soap", "Outdoor furniture", "Beach access"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Living room", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Sofa bed", "Air conditioning", "TV", "Wifi", "Beach essentials", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Resort access", "Elevator", "Clothing storage", "Waterfront", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens"]}, {"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Cooking bas