  ('next-seaview-studio', 'Next Seaview Studio by brege', 'Студия Next Seaview от Brege', 'Welcome to NEXT seaview studio — a stylish apartment in the modern NEXT Apartments residential complex, where every day begins with breathtaking panoramic views of the endless sea.
Whether you''re here for a romantic getaway or a solo retreat, this space is designed for total relaxation: warm sunlight, fresh sea breeze, and a cozy interior create the perfect vacation atmosphere.
Our place is located in a coastal area, just steps away from cafés, beaches, and the scenic promenade.', 'Добро пожаловать в студию NEXT с видом на море — стильную квартиру в современном жилом комплексе NEXT Apartments, где каждый день начинается с захватывающего панорамного вида на бескрайнее море.
Независимо от того, приехали ли вы сюда для романтического отдыха или отдыха в одиночестве, это пространство предназначено для полного расслабления: теплый солнечный свет, свежий морской бриз и уютный интерьер создают идеальную атмосферу для отдыха.
Наше жилье расположено в прибрежной зоне, всего в нескольких шагах от кафе, пляжей и живописной набережной.', 41.63247, 41.60702, 0, 1, 1, 2, '["/apartments/next-seaview-studio/01.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/02.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/03.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/04.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/05.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/06.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/07.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/08.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/09.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/10.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/11.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/12.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/13.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/14.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/15.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/16.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/17.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/18.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/19.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/20.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/21.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/22.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/23.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/24.jpg", "/apartments/next-seaview-studio/25.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Coffee maker", "Microwave", "Mini fridge", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Hot water kettle", "Air conditioning", "Dining table", "Heating", "Queen bed", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Room-darkening shades", "Bed linens", "Essentials", "TV", "Iron", "Body soap", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Cleaning products", "Shampoo", "Washer", "Drying rack for clothing"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 4, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Coffee maker", "Microwave", "Mini fridge", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Hot water kettle"]}, {"room": "Dining area", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Air conditioning", "Dining table", "Heating"]}, {"room": "Bedroom", "photos": 7, "amenities": ["Queen bed", "Air conditioning", "C