  ('sunway-apartment', 'SunWay Apartment by brege', 'Квартира SunWay от brege', 'Wake up to the sound of the sea and watch planes glide above the horizon — all from your private balcony.
This bright and cozy studio is designed for comfort: a fully equipped kitchen, washing machine, air conditioning, and fast Wi-Fi. Perfect for both short and long stays.
Enjoy your morning coffee with a sea view and unwind at sunset as the sky fills with colors and passing planes.', 'Просыпайтесь под шум моря и наблюдайте, как самолеты скользят над горизонтом, — и все это с вашего балкона.
Эта светлая и уютная студия предназначена для комфорта: полностью оборудованная кухня, стиральная машина, кондиционер и быстрый Wi-Fi. Идеально подходит как для краткосрочного, так и длительного проживания.
Насладитесь утренним кофе с видом на море и расслабьтесь на закате, когда небо наполняется красками и пролетающими самолетами.', 41.62274, 41.59552, 0, 1, 1, 2, '["/apartments/sunway-apartment/01.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/02.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/03.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/04.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/05.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/06.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/07.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/08.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/09.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/10.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/11.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/12.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/13.jpg", "/apartments/sunway-apartment/14.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle", "Air conditioning", "Dining table", "Heating", "Double bed", "Clothing storage", "Hangers", "Bed linens", "Room-darkening shades", "TV", "Iron", "Hot water", "Hair dryer", "Beach access", "Outdoor dining area"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Cooking basics", "Stove", "Dishes and silverware", "Refrigerator", "Hot water kettle"]}, {"room": "Dining area", "photos": 1, "amenities": ["Wine glasses", "Air conditioning", "Dining table", "Heating"]}, {"room": "Bedroom", "photos": 4, "amenities": ["Double bed", "Clothing storage", "Air conditioning", "Heating", "Hangers", "Bed linens", "Room-darkening shades", "TV", "Iron"]}, {"room": "Full bathroom", "photos": 3, "amenities": ["Hot water", "Hair dryer"]}, {"room": "Balcony", "photos": 2, "amenities": ["Beach access", "Outdoor dining area"]}, {"room": "Exterior", "photos": 1, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Additional photos", "photos": 1, "amenities": []}]'::jsonb, '1526097932335121078'),
  ('greenside-emerald-apartment', 'Greenside Emerald Apartment by brege', 'Greenside Emerald Apartment от brege', 'Modern 2-bedroom apartment just a minute from the sea in Gonio — the area with the cleanest beach and water near Batumi. 
Includes a full kitchen, cozy living room, and access to seasonal outdoor and indoor pools, a gym, saunas, and an on-site café. 

Perfect for families or friends, this peaceful getaway combines modern comfort with resort-style amenities, all in one of the most beautiful and unspoiled parts of the Black Sea coast.', 'Современная 2-комнатная квартира всего в минуте ходьбы от моря в Гонио — районе с самым чистым пляжем и водой недалеко от Батуми. 
Включает в себя полностью оборудованную кухню, уютную гостиную и доступ к сезонным открытым и закрытым бассейнам, тренажерному залу, саунам и кафе на территории. 

Идеально подходит для семей или друзей, этот спокойный отдых сочетает в себе современный комфорт с удобствами в курортном стиле, все в одном из самых красивых и нетронутых частей побережья Черного моря.', 41.5625, 41.5662, 2, 2, 1, 4, '["/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/01.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/02.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/03.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/04.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/05.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/06.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/07.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/08.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/09.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/10.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/11.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/12.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/13.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/14.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/15.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/16.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/17.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/18.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/19.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/20.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/21.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/22.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/23.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/24.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/25.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/26.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/27.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/28.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/29.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/30.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/31.jpg", "/apartments/greenside-emerald-apartment/32.jpg"]'::jsonb, '["Queen bed"]'::jsonb, '[{"room": "Living room", "photos": 3, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Full kitchen", "photos": 2, "amenities": []}, {"room": "Dining 